The sun gleams off the radiant dial, the shadow cast marking the time the server will reset.
Enter at your own risk!  Full unrestricted PvP lies inside to unsuspecting campers that wish to camp for easy XP.

List of features found inside the Clocktower.


<c√≥  >Bounty Checker: This is to find out who has a Bounty on there Head, an how many bounties that player has received.

Relveler:  Relevels your last two Character Levels(not Legendary Levels).

Desk of Wands:  You can gain another set of wands nomrally given upon character creation from this desk.  Such wands include Dislike, Sequencer, PvP Stats Wand, an other unique wands.

MaxHP:  This will maximize your Character Hit Points.  Only maximizes your Character Levels(not Legendary Levels).  Legendary Levels automatically maximizes upon being booted for edits.  You will be asked to logout so edits can be made to your character's .BIC file.

Heal Me Lever:  This will erase all negative effects from your character.

Legendary Level Room:  This is where you go to continue your levels as you transcend from Character Levels(1-40) into Legendary Levels(40-60).  They are not the same, be warned.  Read ACN Forums for more details or examine the Legendary Book.

Character Deleter:  You can talk to this NPC to delete your character(gone forever an unrecoverable).  You can also use Simtools command !delete at any time an follow the directions in the combat window.

Rebuild All Levels NPC:  This NPC will take all your XP off your character an give it back, thus doing a total level rebuild.  WARNING, you can go invalid due to rare but impossible to fix server engine mistakes.  You cannot rebuild Legendary Levels with this option.  Use XP Bank.

Wings, Tails, Eyes NPC:  Customize your appearance with this NPC.</c>
Enhance all your equippable items(except ammunition) in the Omega Forge.  Payment is with Gold Pieces.  Talk to Shemp if you wish to remove Item Properties from a item.

Deposit an withdraw all your Gold Pieces to your Public CDKey(ID) with the Banker NPC inside.  Acquire XP Keys to enter the XP Bank Room to deposit an withdraw Experience Points for your Public CDKey(ID).

Item Bank has been removed.  Hopefully sometime soon in the future it will return bug-free.

Come to the Market to sell your items in the Loot Splitter(or drop them an they will be sold to the Market).  Items that have been sold by dropping them or using Loot Splitter will be available in the Market NPC's Shop.  Every Hour the inventory is cleaned(to reduce lag).
You can change the name of any equippable item in here by putting the item inthe NPC's chest an talking to the NPC.  Unique color tag applied to denote a change has occured.
Talk to the Linguist inside to learn the differnt languages spoken in Carpathia.  More information about how to speak languages you have learned can be found with the Simtools items.

Enter at your own Risk.  

A Server Message will be shouted for all to know who has entered an exited the Arena.  If you kill someone or someone kills you, a Server Message will display who Won/Lost.  Those that die are auto-resurrected upon death(no need to respawn).  

No Holds Barred Rules inside the Arena.  Server PvP rules do not apply inside the Arena.  

No one will Ranks in Pickpocket Skill will be allowed inside the Arena.

No Bounty Kills or Rewards for gaining a Bounty or Collecting a Bounty is awarded in the Arena.

Inside the Temple, you can buy such items as...


Armor
Weapons
Potions & Scrolls
Jewelry
Many Various Miscellaneous other items from item dye's to Horn's, Harps, Poisions, Traps, etc.
This path takes you to the Level 1-10 maps.  Secret Area lies in here called Azterius Maze.  Your reward for finding the end an defeating Asterius is the key to the Socket Item Shop.

This road takes you to the Level 10-20 maps.  One secret area found here.  It's called Sanctuary of the Souless.  In there in the bottom chamber you can loot for the best ammunition items including Ranged Weapons an Throwing Items.
This is the Level 20-30 maps.  A secret back route to Ravana's Coven can be found here.

This is the Level 30-60 maps.  

Many quest like beyond here.  

You can run the Gauntlet an challenge the Gauntlet Master for a huge XP/GP reward along with a special shop at the end.  

Ravana's Coven is found here as well.  You can find the most powerful items from the Ravana Spectre by recovering Ravana's Eye.  

Also, you can go on a Dracul Quest to find an XP Bank Key to Bank your XP Points.  Many mini quest await to complete this challenge as you seek out an destroy Memnok for his XP Bank Keys.
